{"products":[{"id":15021592510840,"title":"Ranunculus Brushmark Seti®","handle":"ranunculus-brushmark-seti","body_html":"\u003cp\u003eRanunculus Brushmark Seti® is a refined variety with a soft colour change across each petal. At first, the flowers look white, but as they open, the petals show a gentle purple colour towards the edges. The change is smooth, not sharp, giving the flowers a painted, almost watercolour look.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe petals are slightly ruffled and a bit wavy, which adds movement and texture. The blooms are large and full, but less tight than standard ranunculus, giving a softer overall shape.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt also performs well as a cut flower, with strong stems and a good vase life.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat makes it stand out\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhite petals with soft purple edges\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGentle colour change from centre to edge\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSlightly ruffled, wavy petals\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLarge flowers with good impact\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStrong stems with good length\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLong vase life, suitable for bouquets\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAbout the Brushmark range\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePart of the Japanese-bred Ranunculus Novelties line\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSelected for unusual colour and flower form\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMore detailed and expressive than standard types\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eRanunculus Brushmark Seti® works well with whites, lilacs and deeper purples. It’s a good choice if you want something soft but a little different in both the garden and the vase.\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2026-04-30T12:40:42+02:00","created_at":"2026-04-17T22:09:04+02:00","updated_at":"2026-05-12T22:45:41+02:00","vendor":"DutchGrown - EU","product_type":"Ranunculus","tags":["bulb type:Ranunculus","Category:Attracts Bee