_at":"2026-04-17T22:09:20+02:00","product_id":15021592478072,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0557\/2873\/4375\/files\/Ranunculus_Brushmark_Cesar-5.jpg?v=1776456560","width":990,"height":1320}],"options":[{"name":"Order size","position":1,"values":["3","6","12","15"]}]},{"id":15021592445304,"title":"Ranunculus Poodle Ramlia","handle":"ranunculus-poodle-ramlia","body_html":"\u003cp\u003eRanunculus Poodle ‘Ramlia’ is very different from a typical ranunculus. The petals are not smooth and layered. Instead, they are finely cut and almost feathery, which gives the flower a soft, textured look. The blooms feel lighter and a bit more natural, with a slightly fluffy appearance.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe colour is a clean, soft pink that works well with many other shades. Compared to the fuller Romance types, this variety has a more open and airy shape, which makes it stand out straight away.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDespite its softer look, it still has strong stems with good length, making it a good choice for both the garden and cutting.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat makes it different\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eFinely fringed, feather-like petals\u003cbr\u003eSoft, textured and slightly fluffy appearance\u003cbr\u003eMore open and airy shape than standard ranunculus\u003cbr\u003eSoft pink colour that mixes well with other plants\u003cbr\u003eStrong stems with good length\u003cbr\u003eVery suitable for cut flowers and bouquets\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAbout Poodle Ranunculus\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eDeveloped from the same Japanese breeding lines as the Romance series\u003cbr\u003eSelected for texture rather than full, dense flowers\u003cbr\u003eOffers a more relaxed and natural look\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eRanunculus ‘Ramlia’ is a good choice if you want something a bit different. It adds texture and contrast, especially when mixed with fuller flowers.\u003c\/p\u003e"