":"Order size","position":1,"values":["3","6","12","15"]}]},{"id":15021592379768,"title":"Ranunculus Romance™ Salerno","handle":"ranunculus-romance-salerno","body_html":"\u003cp\u003eRanunculus Romance™ ‘Salerno’ is a warm and soft-coloured variety that changes as it grows. The flowers open in peach and apricot shades, sometimes with a hint of salmon. As they mature, the colour fades gently into a lighter, creamy yellow. This natural change gives the plant more interest and variety.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe blooms are large and full, with many layers of petals in the classic ranunculus shape. ‘Salerno’ is part of the Romance series, bred for strong stems and reliable performance.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy gardeners choose it\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLarge, full flowers with a rose-like shape\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWarm peach, apricot and soft salmon tones\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eColour fades gently to a lighter yellow\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAdds warmth and variation to the garden\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStrong stems that stay upright\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eVery good as a cut flower with a long vase life\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEach corm produces several stems\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAbout the Romance series\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNot grown from seed, but selected and grown as clones\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBred for larger, more even flowers\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStronger stems and more reliable results\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eRanunculus ‘Salerno’ works well with soft colours like cream, blush and apricot. It’s a good choice if you want a warm, natural look with gentle colour changes.\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2026-04-30T12:40:39+02:00","created_at":"2026-04-17T22:08:46+02:00","updated_at":"2026-05-12T22:45:41+02:00","vendor":"DutchGrown - EU","product_type":"Ranunculus","tags":["bulb type:Ranunculus","Categ