nd natural look. As they develop, the petals turn a clean, pure white while keeping their full, layered shape. It’s simple, but not plain.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe blooms are large and full, with many layers of petals in the classic ranunculus shape. ‘Montenvers’ is part of the Romance series, bred for strong stems and reliable performance.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy gardeners choose it\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLarge, full flowers with a rose-like shape\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhite petals with a soft green centre when opening\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eClean, fresh colour that works with any planting style\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStrong stems that stay upright\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eVery good as a cut flower with a long vase life\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEach corm produces several stems\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAbout the Romance series\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNot grown from seed, but selected and grown as clones\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBred for larger, more even flowers\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStronger stems and more reliable results\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eRanunculus ‘Montenvers’ is a good choice if you want a simple white that still has interest and works well both in the garden and in a vase.\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2026-04-30T12:40:37+02:00","created_at":"2026-04-17T22:08:46+02:00","updated_at":"2026-05-12T22:45:41+02:00","vendor":"DutchGrown - EU","product_type":"Ranunculus","tags":["bulb type:Ranunculus","Category:Attracts Bees \u0026 Butterflies","Category:Cut Flower Use","Category:Ideal for pots","Category:Indoor Growing","colour:green","colour:white","Fall Planted Bulbs","fall_planted","Ranunculus","Ranunculus_Romance","season:Early Summer"],"variants":[{"id":55534396801400,"title":"3","option1":"3","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"754","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"availabl