:"2026-04-17T22:09:02+02:00","product_id":15021592281464,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0557\/2873\/4375\/files\/Ranunculus_Romance_Montenvers-2_18d86f28-fbfb-4cc9-aa05-5d4dc3a52b42.jpg?v=1776456542","width":990,"height":1320}],"options":[{"name":"Order size","position":1,"values":["3","6","12","15"]}]},{"id":15021592248696,"title":"Ranunculus Romance™ Gascogne","handle":"ranunculus-romance-gascogne","body_html":"\u003cp\u003eRanunculus Romance™ ‘Gascogne’ is a good choice if you want something different from the usual pinks and whites. The flowers are a soft lavender-purple with a hint of lilac, and the colour can change slightly in different light. It’s a calm, balanced shade that stands out without being too strong.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe blooms are large and full, with many layers of petals in the classic ranunculus shape. ‘Gascogne’ is part of the Romance series, bred for strong stems and reliable performance.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy gardeners choose it\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLarge, full flowers with a rose-like shape\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSoft lavender-purple colour with lilac tones\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA less common shade that mixes well with other colours\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStrong stems that stay upright\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eVery good as a cut flower with a long vase life\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEach corm produces several stems\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAbout the Romance series\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNot grown from seed, but selected and grown as clones\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBred for larger, more even flowers\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStronger stems and more reliable results\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eRanunculus ‘Gascogne’ works well with whites, soft pinks, apricot tones and deeper purples. It’s a good option if you want something a little different but still easy to 